def min_subarray_len(nums, target):
    total_sum = 0
    start = 0
    min_len = float('inf')
    for end in range(len(nums)):
        total_sum += nums[end]
        while total_sum >= target:
            min_len = min(min_len, end - start + 1)
            total_sum -= nums[start]
            start += 1
    return min_len if min_len != float('inf') else 0
